{{rfp.sentDate}}

Dear {{supplier.contact.firstName}},

{{buyer.contact.company.name}} is pleased to announce that you have been selected for inclusion in our {{rfp.programYear}} Hotel bidding and selection process.

{{supplier.contact.firstName}}, because of the amount of travel spend {{buyer.company.name}} has in your hotel and city, we are inviting you to submit a rate and amenity package for our consideration. If accepted, your hotel will be one of a carefully chosen number of properties that will be included in our hotel program. Supporting {{buyer.company.name}} corporate travel policy, employee travelers will be utilizing an on-line booking tool that filters for only preferred vendors and contracts. An incorrect number will exclude your hotel from the preferred listing that employees will be selecting from for reservations.

Your submission will be evaluated on the following criteria:

  • Rate should be a minimum of 15% below published corporate rate or at least 10% below the Consortia Rate.
  • Rate should be competitive with those offered to other corporate accounts with similar spending potential
  • Rate will be net, non-commissionable.
  • Rate is run-of-the-house with last room availability (excluding suites, concierge, club and tower rooms).

There are three value-added amenities that will assist your bid greatly:

  • Complimentary Breakfast (continental, full or buffet)
  • Waiver of telephone access fees for local, long-distance and toll free calls;
  • Waiver of wireless or broadband cable internet fees.

There are two other requirements that {{buyer.company.name}} has mandated.

  • Selected hotels must agree to provide monthly room night volume reports. An electronic form will be sent at the end of each month for you to complete.
  • Selected hotel rates will be audited to assure compliance to contracted rates. Selected hotels must agree to pay the difference when disparities occur. As an example: If your hotels contracted rate for {{buyer.company.name}} is $145.00 and the audit shows a booking at $185.00 (when hotel had availability), hotel agrees to pay the difference.

To assist you in determining the {{rfp.programYear}} {{buyer.company.name}} Rate, be sure to consider the attached room night volumes by city during the period of {{rfp.programStartDate}} through {{rfp.programEndDate}}.

Please complete the following hotel questionnaire and should you have any questions regarding our RFP, please contact (3rd party) at the phone number listed above.

We are confident that {{rfp.programYear}} will be a most successful year for both our program and our valued hotel partners. We respectfully await your reply and look forward to the opportunity to work with your hotel in {{rfp.programYear}} .

Sincerely,
{{buyer.contact.fullName}}  
{{buyer.contact.jobTitle}} 
{{buyer.contact.company.name}} 
{{buyer.contact.email}} 
{{buyer.contact.phone}}
